To download these themes:
========================
Click the download button at http://github.com/madsailor/XBMC-Plymouth-Bootsplash-Screens and choose tar.bz or zip archive and follow readme in the folder of the theme you want to install

or

1)Install git if you havn't already: sudo apt-get install git
2)Run: cd ~/Desktop to change to your desktop directory (or use another convenient location)
3)Run: git clone git://github.com/madsailor/XBMC-Plymouth-Bootsplash-Screens
4)Follow the readme for the theme you want in the XBMC Plymouth Bootsplash Screens folder on your desktop
5)Enjoy!
